==French==

===Pronunciation===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /pʁe.fe.ʁe/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /pRe.fe.Re/

===Verb===
'''préférer'''

# to [[prefer]]

====Usage Note====
In the [[je]], [[tu]], [[il]], and [[ils]] [[conjugation]]s, the second é (e with an accent [[aigu]]) becomes è (e with an accent grave) (i.e. je ''préfère'', tu ''préfères'', il ''préfère'', ils ''préfèrent'').

